**Neu (Redesign):** **Dashboard:** **`.dashboard-intent`**, **`.dashboard-intent__heading`**, **`.dashboard-intent__grid`** (alle drei Sektionen: Kachel-Raster; **`__stack`** nur noch optional in CSS, nicht im Dashboard-Template), **`.dashboard-intent-tile`** (+ **`__icon`**, **`__body`**, **`__title`**, **`__meta`**, **`__chev`**), **`dashboard-intent-tile--static`**. **Bereinigung:** **`.cleanup-step-nav`** (+ **`__counter`**, **`__actions`**); **`.events-cleanup-hint`**, **`.cleanup-undo-form`**. **Legacy (CSS, ggf. unbenutzt):** **`.dashboard-next-event*`**, **`card--dash-tile*`**, **`.dashboard-card-link`**, **`.dashboard-hygiene-rows`**, **`.dashboard-row-link`** (+ **`--block-start`**) — `REDESIGN.md` §5.2. **`.tool-surface`** auf **`card.card--filter`** (`REDESIGN.md` §5.2.2). **Tool-Strip (verbindlich):** **`disclosure`** in **`card--filter`** + **`.tool-strip__actions`** für reine Aktionen; **`form`** + **`.form-actions`** wenn Eingabefelder — Spec **§5.2.3**; Events-Index + Event-Detail-Planung: **sessionStorage**-Keys und Standard **eingeklappt** in **`REDESIGN.md` §5.2.3**. **`.context-actions`** (+ `__title`, `__buttons`) — **Legacy** / Sonderfall; HTML §5.2.1. **`.settings-nav`** (+ `__section`, `__section-title`, `__list`, `__row`, `__icon`, `__meta`, `__label`, `__description`, `__badge`, `__chevron`). **`.user-menu`** (+ **`__summary`**, **`__panel`**, **`__list`**, **`__link`**, **`__link--danger`**, **`__sep`**, optional **`__badge`**). **`.empty-state`** (+ `__icon`, `__message`, optional **`--filtered`**). **`[hidden]`** in **`base.css`** mit **`display: none !important`** (Kompatibilität mit **`.empty-state`** **`display: flex`**). **`.page-back`** (Zurück-Link, `base.css`). **`.billbro-workflow`** (+ `__step`, `__step--done`, `__step--current`, `__index`). **`.events-ratings-others-table`** (+ **`__col-member`**, **`__col-score`**, **`__col-highlight`**, **`__highlight-text`**, **`__dash`**, **`__row--current`**). **`.event-ratings-all`** / **`__heading`**, **`.event-ratings-toolbar`** (+ **`__hint`**, **`__actions`**); Anker **`#event-ratings-form`**, **`#event-ratings-actions`**, **`#event-ratings-all`**. **Events-Statistiken (Tab):** **`.events-stats-restaurant-block`** (+ **`__heading`**, **`__caption`**), **`.events-stats-restaurant-ratings-table`**, **`.events-stats-sort-btn`** (+ **`--active`**), **`.events-stats-inline-rating`**; JSON-Keys **`restaurantRatings`**, **`organizerRatings`** (`#events-monatsessen-charts-data`).

Vor neuer Klasse: Registry in `REDESIGN.md` prüfen; Duplikate vermeiden.

## Wesentliche UX-Entscheidungen

Bei Tab-Splits, Primäraktionen, neuer Navigation, neuen Komponenten: **2–3 Optionen** mit Begründung an den User (siehe Heuristiken in `REDESIGN.md`), **Empfehlung** aussprechen.
